-- Mathematical Framework: MCDA (AHP weights), FMEA RPN, CPM/RCPSP DAG scheduling,
--                        Shannon entropy coverage optimization, Pareto frontier selection,
--                        Biomorphic wave-based evolutionary generations
-- Covers: 12 GAPs → 28 tasks → 5 waves → 4 supervisory layers → 12 days
-- STAMP: SC-ZMOF-001, SC-ARCH-SPLIT-001, SC-GLM-UI-001..010, SC-SIL4-006,
--        SC-SAFETY-001..022, SC-MUDA-001, SC-FUNC-001..008, SC-CPU-GOV-001
-- Date: 2026-04-05
