-- =============================================================================
-- §8. SHANNON ENTROPY TRAJECTORY
-- =============================================================================

-- C1-C8 gold standard categories as probability distribution.
-- H = -Σ(p_i × log2(p_i)), max H = log2(8) = 3.0 bits for uniform distribution.
--
-- BEFORE (current state):
--   C1 Page Structure:  p=0.95  (Lustre SSR works)
--   C2 Status Badges:   p=0.80  (hardcoded but visible)
--   C3 Data Grids:      p=0.70  (grids render, data fake)
--   C4 Timeline:        p=0.50  (timestamps exist, not ordered from real data)
--   C5 Interactive:     p=0.05  (buttons exist but are no-ops)
--   C6 Media/Rich:      p=0.60  (sparklines render)
--   C7 AI Advisory:     p=0.10  (AG-UI types exist, SSE broken)
--   C8 Action Button:   p=0.01  (Guardian types exist, not wired)
--
--   Normalized: p_i = coverage_i / Σcoverage_i
--   p = [0.256, 0.215, 0.189, 0.135, 0.013, 0.162, 0.027, 0.003]
--   H_before = 2.42 bits (BELOW 2.5 threshold)
--
-- AFTER Wave 4 (target):
--   C1: p=0.95  C2: p=0.90  C3: p=0.85  C4: p=0.80
--   C5: p=0.85  C6: p=0.70  C7: p=0.80  C8: p=0.75
--
--   p = [0.148, 0.140, 0.132, 0.125, 0.132, 0.109, 0.125, 0.117]
--   H_after = 2.98 bits (ABOVE 2.5 threshold, near maximum 3.0)
--
-- Delta H = +0.56 bits (23% improvement)
-- Entropy increase per wave: ~0.14 bits/wave (monotonic)

