-- SIL-6 constraint satisfaction per wave:
--
-- Wave 0: +SC-ZENOH-001 (NIF loaded), +SC-NIF-001 (FFI safety),
--         +SC-SEC-001 (auth middleware)                        = 20%
-- Wave 1: +SC-ZMOF-001 (Zenoh sole transport), +SC-ARCH-SPLIT-001 (Gleam→Rust),
